		<title>Professor James Wren, Of Baylor University Releases Book and Recommends ExhibitView Software</title>
		<link>http://emailwire.podbean.com/2012/03/14/professor-james-wren-of-baylor-university-releases-book-and-recommends-exhibitview-software/</link>
