<p>EmailWire.Com currently offers Web 2.0 unlimited <span style="color: #000080;"><span lang="zxx"><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="http://www.emailwire.com/publications/unlimited_press_release_distribution.php"><span style="font-family: Verdana,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">SEO press release distribution</span></span></a></span></span></span><span style="font-family: Verdana,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: small;"> for $999 per year, $599 for six months or $99/month at </span></span></p>
