			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">Welcome to GroupWeb Radio – a weekly podcast for CEO profiles, business news and press releases</p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">I am Michelle Polins for GroupWeb Radio</p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">Each day we read business breaking news as it is published on EmailWire.Com - a global newswire and press release distribution service for businesses, authors, organizations and government agencies. We interview CEOs, business owners or managers about their products and services or causes. These interviews are published as podcasts and embedded in press releases that are distributed throughout U.S. and global media outlets. These podcasts will also be available on iTune, podcast directories and mobile phones. For more information, go to <span style="color: #000080;"><span lang="zxx"><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="http://www.emailwire.com/podcast">www.emailwire.com/podcast</a><a href="http://www.emailwire.com/"> </a></span></span></span>or call 281-645-4086.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">
</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0in;"><em><strong>London, United Kingdom </strong></em>– The largest independent international Financial Advisory firm, the <span style="color: #000080;"><span lang="zxx"><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="http://www.devere-group.com/">deVere Group</a></span></span></span>, is pleased to announce an impressive conclusion for 2009, including a strong close to the year in the last quarter.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">Nigel Green, founder and CEO of the deVere Group said: “Our strong business and financial performance in 2009 positions us well for the year ahead and we will continue to remain focused on our strategy of excellence in maintaining high standards of client services, global expansion and technology leadership within the industry.” You can find more information on deVere at <span style="color: #000080;"><span lang="zxx"><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="http://www.devere-group.com/">www.devere-group.com</a></span></span></span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0in;">
</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0in;"><em><strong>Detroit, MI</strong></em> – Starting an auto detailing service with growing franchise company, DetailXPerts, has a good opportunity for people transitioning form the military, recent college graduates and people laid-off by the automobile industry and other major industries. DetailXPerts is a growing company with plans to award new franchises across the U.S. in 2010. For more information, go to <span style="color: #000080;"><span lang="zxx"><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="http://www.detailxperts.net/">www.detailxperts.net/</a></span></span></span>.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0in;" align="center">
</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0in;" align="left"><span style="font-size: small;"><em><strong>San Francisco, CA -</strong></em></span><span style="font-size: small;"> Market Deals today announced the release of Market Deals 1.0, a location aware marketing solution for the retail industry that facilitates geo targeting of promotions. Designed to help increase foot traffic to local stores, Market Deals allows retailers to quickly and dynamically advertise product promotions through a patent pending technology (Internet+™). For more information, go to </span><span style="color: #000080;"><span lang="zxx"><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a href="http://www.marketdeals.com/"><span style="font-size: small;">www.marketdeals.com</span></a></span></span></span><span style="font-size: small;">. </span></p>
